Educenter Hugo | Demo | Page Speed (86%)

Features

  • Multiple language support (Fr, En)
  • Google analytics support
  • CSS and Js bundle with hugo pipe
  • Netlify settings predefine
  • Forestry cms pre-configured
  • Multiple author available
  • Contact form Support
  • Mailchimp integrate
  • GDPR consent enable
  • Google map support
  • Top header customization
  • Taxonomy or category
  • Google page speed optimized ( 86% )
  • Open graph meta tag
  • Twitter card meta tag

Local development

# clone the repository
git clone git@github.com:themefisher/educenter-hugo.git

# cd in the project directory
$ cd educenter-hugo/exampleSite/

# Start local dev server
$ hugo server --themesDir ../..

Or Check out Full Documentation.

Content Management System

This project has been pre-configured to work with Forestry a git-based CMS, import your repository in Forestry and you will be able to edit and preview your site ✨.

Any changes you make in Forestry will be committed back to the repo and deployed if you use Netlify. ## Deployment and hosting
